        "faq_item_U8Vae4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does the guarantee work?",
            "content": "<p><strong>Our 100% Shade Match Guarantee:</strong> We want you to test your new foundation without any risk. If the formula does not adapt perfectly to your skin tone, you will receive 100% of your money back—no questions asked.</p>",
            "faq_show_image": false,
            "faq_enable_popup": false,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
            "faq_popup_content": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_BaHyjk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Description",
            "content": "<p>Experience a foundation that does the work for you. This white cream transforms upon application to match your unique skin tone perfectly. The hydrating formula provides buildable coverage that hides redness and imperfections while remaining weightless and breathable all day.</p>",
            "faq_show_image": false,
            "faq_enable_popup": false,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
            "faq_popup_content": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_m8GzcM": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does this work for my skin?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Our adaptive formula is suitable for all fair to medium skin tones and is specifically formulated for mature skin types. It is designed to float over fine lines and wrinkles rather than settling into them, making it ideal for skin with texture, rosacea, or age spots.</p>",
            "faq_show_image": true,
            "faq_image": "shopify://shop_images/Untitled_design_9.png",
            "faq_enable_popup": false,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
            "faq_popup_content": ""
          }
        },
        "faq_item_fkJYQr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Ingredients",
            "content": "<p>Contains nourishing, skin-first ingredients: </p><p><strong>1. Glycerin</strong> - Attracts moisture for a soft, supple feel.</p><p><strong>2. Bisabolol & Tone-Evening Pigments</strong> - Help reduce the appearance of redness and uneven tone for a more balanced, natural-looking complexion.</p><p><strong>3. Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E)</strong> - Nourishes and supports a fresh, healthy-looking complexion.</p>",
            "faq_show_image": false,
            "faq_enable_popup": true,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
            "faq_popup_content": "<p>Aqua, Cyclopentasiloxane, Glycerin, Titanium Dioxide, Butylene Glycol, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Cetyl Peg/Ppg-10/1, Dimethicone, C12-15 Alkyl Benzoate, Butylene Glycol Dicaprylate/Dicaprate, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Methyl Hydrogenated Rosinate, Dimethicone, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Phenylbenzimidazole Sulfonic Acid, Sodium Chloride, Tocopheryl Acetate, Bisabolol, Hydroxyacetophenone, Lecithin, Buddleja Officinalis Extract, Isopropyl Myristate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Stearic Acid, BHT, Propanediol, Methicone, Silica, Aluminum Hydroxide, Dimethicone/Vinyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Silica Silylate, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Aminomethyl Propanol, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Phenoxyethanol, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Isostearic Acid, Sodium Citrate, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Polyester-1, Disodium Edta, Mica, Alumina, Parfum, Ci 77891, Ci 77492, Ci 77491, Ci 77499</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_TgaEiB": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Shipping & Returns",
            "content": "<p><strong>Love It or It's Free.</strong> Try it for 30 days. If it doesn't float over your lines or match your shade exactly as promised, just let us know for a full refund.</p><p><strong>Fast & Secure Delivery.</strong> We ship your order within 1 business day. Free shipping on all orders over $[threshold]. Tracked shipping so you know exactly when your glow arrives.</p><p><strong>Zero-Stress Returns.</strong> No complicated forms. No hidden fees. If you aren't happy, we aren't happy. Just reach out to our friendly support team for a quick resolution.</p>",
            "faq_show_image": false,
            "faq_enable_popup": false,
            "faq_popup_trigger_text": "View full list",
            "faq_popup_title": "FULL LIST OF INGREDIENTS",
            "faq_popup_content": ""
          }
        },
